h death everyday. A young discovery channel journalist approaches his team to cover bomb squad story but falls in love with him.','Hindi','India','13 wins & 18 nominations.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTUyMzM5OTM5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTIwMjA3OA@@._V1_SX300.jpg',0,6.9,38,'tt2176013','movie','True',1,1449249681,1449249681),(10,'The Internship',2013,'PG-13','07 Jun 2013','119 min','Comedy','Shawn Levy','Vince Vaughn (screenplay), Jared Stern (screenplay','Vince Vaughn, Owen Wilson, Rose Byrne, Aasif Mandv','Two salesmen whose careers have been torpedoed by the digital age find their way into a coveted internship at Google, where they must compete with a group of young, tech-savvy geniuses for a shot at employment.','English, Tagalog, Ca','USA','1 nomination.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMjM1MzczMDgwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDM4NjM2OQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg',42,6.3,149,'tt2234155','movie','True',1,1449250230,1449250230),(11,'Goliyon Ki Rasleela Ram-Leela',2013,'N/A','15 Nov 2013','150 min','Drama, Musical, Romance','Sanjay Leela Bhansali','Sanjay Leela Bhansali (screenplay), Garima (screen','Deepika Padukone, Ranveer Singh, Supriya Pathak, S','Ram and Leela, their love, lust and the drama afterwards. Modern adaptation of William Shakespeare\'s \'Romeo & Juliet\'.','Hindi','India','29 wins & 90 nominations.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BOTI0MzEyODgyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI3Mjk3MDE@._V1_SX300.jpg',0,6.2,10,'tt2215477','movie','True',1,1449250595,1449250595),(12,'Steve Jobs',2015,'R','23 Oct 2015','122 min','Biography, Drama','Danny Boyle','Aaron Sorkin (screenplay), Walter Isaacson (book)','Michael Fassbender, Kate Winslet, Seth Rogen, Jeff','His passion and ingenuity have been the driving force behind the digital age. However his drive to revolutionize technology was sacrificial. Ultimately it affected his family life and possibly his health. In this revealing film we explore the trials and triumphs of a modern day genius, the late CEO of Apple inc. St